    <h3>Layer Selection</h3>
    <p>In order to visualise a product we first have to activate it in the Favourite Layer Selection Window.</p>
    <p>We have just opened it, you can see it on the left side of the screen.</p>
    <p>You can open and close it at any time by clicking in the navigation bar (top of the screen) on the <i class="fa fa-fw fa-globe"/> Favourite Layers button.</p>
    <p>You can move the window to another position by clicking and dragging on its header.</p>
    <p>We also selected a bounding box of interes you can now see on the globe, only data inside this bbox wil be loaded.</p>
    <p>The bounding box can be manually selected by clicking on Tools and selecting the bounding box tool.>/p>
    <p>A product can be activated by clicking on its corresponding check box, we will do this now.</p>
</section>
